Package edu.uab.ssg.io.limdi

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CovariateTabParser.RecordListener
    A listener for handling parsed sample records and problems due to bad record formatting.
    CovariateTabParser.SampleRecord
    A sample record.
    DoseTabParser.RecordListener
    A listener for handling parsed sample records and problems due to bad record formatting.
    DoseTabParser.SampleRecord
    A sample record.
    GenotypeFileParser.GenotypeRecord
    A genotype record.
    GenotypeFileParser.RecordListener
    A listener for handling parsed genotype records and problems due to bad record formatting.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CovariateTabParser
    A parser for the tab-delimited text file, called Data_jelai_25March_09.tab, containing the covariate data for the Limdi warfarin analysis.
    DoseTabParser
    A parser for the tab-delimited text file, called GWAS_AA_feb19_09_B109.tab, containing the dose data for the Limdi warfarin analysis.
    GenotypeFileParser
    A parser for the genotype file format used by the Genome Sciences Genotyping and Resequencing Center (GS GRC) to report genotyping results from an Illumina Infinium 1M Duo V3 SNP array.
